  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This clinical observational study investigates the incidence of wound healing abnormalities
      in patients undergoing major abdominal surgery. Second aim of the study is, if wound healing
      deficits may be accompanied by abnormalities in blood coagulation parameters.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
