    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age &gt;= 18 years

          -  Male or female

          -  Informed consent

          -  Major abdominal surgery

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pre-existing coagulation abnormalities

          -  Pre-existing severe renal or liver failure

          -  Chemo- or radiochemotherapy
